title: Story Time with Farm Animals at Farrel-McWhirter Park | Seattle Area Family Fun Calendar | ParentMap
text:
Fri, January 24, 2025 —
Fri, January 24, 2025 —
(Ages 0-5) Snuggle up with some furry farm friends for Storytime in the Barn. We will celebrate all things farm with fun, engaging stories, and you'll get to meet one of the farm animals. Great introduction to farm animals.
Reminders:
- Activity fee is for an adult/child pair. Please register the child.
- Participants should wear close toed shoes and dress for the weather. Activities run rain or shine.
Image sourced from event website.
